":303936.0,"held_pct_insiders":0.74134004,"held_pct_institutions":0.12537,"beta":1.461,"fifty_two_week_high":1717.9,"fifty_two_week_low":900.0,"fifty_day_average":1024.665,"two_hundred_day_avg":1256.955,"recommendation":"none","all_time_high":1903.0,"all_time_low":900.0,"long_business_summary":"JSL Industries Limited manufactures and sells engineering goods in India. The company offers instrument transformers, such as cast resin indoor and outdoor type instrument transformers, outdoor metering units, outdoor CT and PT products, and cast resin components for switchgears; and LT switchboards, including custom-built power control and motor control centers, auto transformer starters, magnastart systems, distribution boards, and bus-ducts, as well as feeder, control, relay, and APFC panels. It also provides L.T. air circuit breakers; air break starters comprising DOL and star delta starter, single phase and three phase DOL/star-delta submersible pump controllers; oil-immersed starters and pump controllers; and shaft, induction, screen protected drip proof, and textile motors, as well as mono-block pumps. The company offers its products to engineering consultants, utilities, public sector organizations, various governments/semi-governments, and private industries. JSL Industries Limited was incorporated in 1966 and is based in Mogar, India."}}